'''波尔菲里耶'''（{{lang-sr-cyr|Порфирије}}，{{lang-sr-latn|Porfirije}}，{{lang-en|Porphyrius}}；出生名'''Prvoslav Perić'''，{{bd|1961年|7月22日}}），[[塞尔维亚正教会|塞尔维亚正教会]]第46任[[牧首|牧首]]。2021年2月18日，波尔菲里耶于[[圣萨瓦教堂|圣萨瓦教堂]]接替了去世三个月的[[爱任纽_(塞尔维亚牧首)|爱任纽]]，正式成为第46任牧首<ref>{{cite web |title=Metropolitan Porfirije of Zagreb and Ljubljana elected for a new Patriarch of Serbia |url=http://spc.rs/eng/metropolitan_porphyry_zagreb_and_ljubljana_elected_new_patriarch_serbia |website=spc.rs |access-date=2021-02-19 |archive-date=2021-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218172131/http://www.spc.rs/eng/metropolitan_porphyry_zagreb_and_ljubljana_elected_new_patriarch_serbia |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Metropolitan Porfirije Of Zagreb And Ljubljana Elected For A New Patriarch Of Serbia |url=https://cordmagazine.com/news/metropolitan-porfirije-of-zagreb-and-ljubljana-elected-for-a-new-patriarch-of-serbia/ |website=cordmagazine.com |access-date=2021-02-19 |archive-date=2021-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218171507/https://cordmagazine.com/news/metropolitan-porfirije-of-zagreb-and-ljubljana-elected-for-a-new-patriarch-of-serbia/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Serbian Church Elects Patriarch Deemed Close to President |url=https://balkaninsight.com/2021/02/18/serbian-church-elects-patriarch-deemed-close-to-president/ |website=balkaninsight.com |access-date=2021-02-19 |archive-date=2021-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218161412/https://balkaninsight.com/2021/02/18/serbian-church-elects-patriarch-deemed-close-to-president/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Serbian Orthodox Church elects new patriarch |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/serbia-patriarch-idINKBN2AI2CR |website=reuters.com |access-date=2021-02-19 |archive-date=2021-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221024532/https://www.reuters.com/article/serbia-patriarch-idINKBN2AI2CR |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

